text.tspan: Welcome to our digital collection of 4,444 unique Noobz non-fungible tokens
on the Solana blockchain. Mint your own Noobz NFT to be a member of the
Noobz Only Leisure Club. This place for good vibes will serve as community
headquarters to exchange ideas on the future of the project The Noobz NFT
public sale 2/22/2022. Noobz are minted using the fair distribution method
at a cost of .222 SOL. Each Noobz NFT is generated from 300 hand drawn
traits and stored on the Solana (SOL) blockchain. 44 Noobz will be held for
team thank you and community giveaways. Join our Discord for project news.
